'''伊斯蘭軍'''（{{lang-ar|جيش الإسلام}}，Jaysh al-Islam）是[[叙利亚内战|叙利亚内战]]中的一個武裝組織，由多個[[伊斯蘭主義|伊斯蘭主義]]和[[賽萊菲|薩拉菲主義]]武裝單位聯盟而成。<ref name="reuters1oct">{{Cite news|title=Insight: Saudi Arabia boosts Salafist rivals to al Qaeda in Syria|url=http://www.reuters.com/article/2013/10/01/us-syria-crisis-jihadists-insight-idUSBRE9900RO20131001|agency=Reuters|date=1 October 2013|accessdate=8 May 2015|archive-date=2015-05-18|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150518074336/http://www.reuters.com/article/2013/10/01/us-syria-crisis-jihadists-insight-idUSBRE9900RO20131001}}</ref>它主要在[[大馬士革|大馬士革]]附近活動。<ref name="rise">{{Cite news|title=Rise of Jaish al-Islam marks a turn in Syria conflict|url=http://www.middleeasteye.net/news/jaish-al-islam-piece-918366283|agency=Middle East Eye|date=7 May 2015|accessdate=8 May 2015|archive-date=2015-05-09|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150509024917/http://www.middleeasteye.net/news/jaish-al-islam-piece-918366283|dead-url=no}}</ref>伊斯蘭軍是該區域最大的反政府武裝勢力。<ref>{{Cite news|title=Syria army 'tightens siege of rebel bastion near Damascus'|url=https://uk.news.yahoo.com/syria-army-tightens-siege-rebel-bastion-near-damascus-131606250.html|agency=AFP|date=3 May 2015|accessdate=11 May 2015|archive-date=2017-10-19|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20171019093844/https://uk.news.yahoo.com/syria-army-tightens-siege-rebel-bastion-near-damascus-131606250.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>伊斯蘭軍是附屬於「伊斯蘭陣線」的一分子，<ref name="BBC22Nov"/>而「伊斯蘭陣線」拒絕加入受西方國家支持的[[自由敘利亞軍|自由敘利亞軍]]。<ref name="telegraph5dec">{{Cite news|title=Leading Syrian rebels defect, dealing blow to fight against al-Qaeda|url=http://www.telegraph.co.uk/news/worldnews/middleeast/syria/10498477/Leading-Syrian-rebels-defect-dealing-blow-to-fight-against-al-Qaeda.html|work=Daily Telegraph|date=5 December 2013|accessdate=5 December 2013|archive-date=2018-06-13|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180613090121/https://www.telegraph.co.uk/news/worldnews/middleeast/syria/10498477/Leading-Syrian-rebels-defect-dealing-blow-to-fight-against-al-Qaeda.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>

==歷史==
===伊斯蘭旅===
伊斯蘭軍的前身「伊斯蘭旅」由[[扎哈蘭·阿魯什|扎哈蘭·阿魯什]]於2011年中創立。<ref name=FreedomfighterCannibals>{{cite news|url=http://www.independent.co.uk/news/world/middle-east/freedom-fighters-cannibals-the-truth-about-syrias-rebels-8662618.html|title=Freedom fighters? Cannibals? The truth about Syria’s rebels|author=Aron Lund|publisher=The Independent|date=17 June 2013|accessdate=7 November 2013|archive-date=2015-07-19|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150719153319/http://www.independent.co.uk/news/world/middle-east/freedom-fighters-cannibals-the-truth-about-syrias-rebels-8662618.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>

===合併===
2013年9月29日，在大馬士革周圍活動的50個反政府武裝團體宣佈合併為單一團體「伊斯蘭軍」，而它們當中以「伊斯蘭旅」的實力較強，所以由「伊斯蘭旅」的首領[[扎哈蘭·阿魯什|扎哈蘭·阿魯什]]擔任「伊斯蘭軍」的領導人。<ref name="fp1oct">{{Cite news|title=The Army of Islam Is Winning in Syria|url=http://foreignpolicy.com/2013/10/01/the-army-of-islam-is-winning-in-syria/|work=Foreign Policy Magazine|date=1 October 2013|accessdate=8 May 2015|archive-date=2022-03-19|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220319195257/https://foreignpolicy.com/2013/10/01/the-army-of-islam-is-winning-in-syria/}}</ref><ref name="yt">{{Cite news|title=Total of 43 Islamist Groups Unite under Newly Formed "Army of Islam" in Syria|agency=YouTube|url=https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=nIjtc6At-CU|4=|date=29 September 2013|accessdate=7 November 2013|archive-date=2016-04-03|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160403155347/https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=nIjtc6At-CU|dead-url=no}}</ref>至2013年11月，約60個團體已併入「伊斯蘭軍」。<ref name="aawsat12Nov">{{Cite news|title=Syria: Jaysh Al-Islam rejects Geneva II conference|url=http://www.aawsat.net/2013/11/article55322150|work=Asharq Al-Awsat|date=12 November 2013|accessdate=15 November 2013|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20131115173809/http://www.aawsat.net/2013/11/article55322150|archivedate=2013年11月15日}}</ref>

===近況===
2015年12月25日，[[扎哈蘭·阿魯什|扎哈蘭·阿魯什]]在大馬士革市郊被敘政府軍空襲炸死。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.bbc.co.uk/news/world-middle-east-35178684|title=Syria conflict: Jaysh al-Islam rebel leaders die in air strike|work=BBC News|date=2015-12-26|accessdate=2016-01-01|archive-date=2015-12-25|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151225170353/http://www.bbc.co.uk/news/world-middle-east-35178684|dead-url=no}}</ref>Essam al-Buwaydhani繼任「伊斯蘭軍」的軍事領導人。

2016年4月28日，伊斯蘭軍與[[努斯拉陣線|努斯拉陣線]]領導的武裝分子在東[[乌塔大马士革|古塔]]激戰，至5月中已造成超過300名戰鬥人員喪生。<ref>{{Cite news |url=http://www.dailymail.co.uk/wires/afp/article-3591272/Rebel-infighting-near-Syria-capital-kills-hundreds-monitor.html |title=Rebel infighting near Syria capital kills hundreds: monitor |work=Daily Mail Online |date=2016-05-15 |accessdate=2016-05-21 |archive-date=2020-11-08 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201108110508/https://www.dailymail.co.uk/wires/afp/article-3591272/Rebel-infighting-near-Syria-capital-kills-hundreds-monitor.html }}</ref>

